{
  "stem": "7157.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there we were, like, spending all day in a, in this apartment, without even being able to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so George and I, of course, were very, very close.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, we spent, you know, 24 hours a day, you know, there was no school, there was no, no diversions of any sort.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was just the two of us together, always, in, during this time frame in the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, anyway, just to go on, there was a, I know I'm not giving you any chance to ask questions, Bernie.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] To go on, there was a time, you know, there was a time frame where all of a sudden, we started hearing gunshots and cannons and airplanes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, for us this was good news, because we-- there was no such thing as a newspaper that would tell you what's going on in the war.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had no idea what was going on at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This-- at least at this point.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we heard this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we got very nervous about it, because there were a lot of rumors the Russians were coming, Russians were coming.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were afraid that if the Russians came into these small villages, then we just didn't know what would happen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we decided to go to Warsaw, to Szutka, Wujek's sister's, house, and go there and see if we could spend the time there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We, we felt at this point, it might be safer to be in a big city, OK.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Big mistake, it turned out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But anyway, that's what we decided.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because while we went to the city-- this was now, again, 1944, to give a time frame-- the uprising started, the Polish Warsaw uprising.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
